  "_comment": "Server-side source of truth for which role is responsible for each document section, per pack. The backend analyses endpoint reads this to filter returned analyses by role. Keep in sync with the assignedTo arrays in ui/src/lib/workflowPacks/*.js. coordinatorRoles lists roles with canManage:true that always see all documents.",
